OL,3,CLondon mayor rules out expansion of
OL,4,CUlez if he stays in role after election
OL,6,F"But my commitment to Londoners is
OL,7,Fthis will not include a new pay-per-
OL,8,Fmile road user charging scheme or
OL,9,Famending the standards for the Ulez
OL,10,Fscheme.
OL,12,F"The introduction and expansion of the
OL,13,FUlez has been necessary and effective.
OL,14,FBut now it's in place and working, I
OL,15,Fwill ensure the goalposts are not
OL,16,Fmoved for drivers."
