OL,6,FMr Khan adds in the letter that he
OL,7,Fwould focus on other measures to
OL,8,Ftackle air pollution, including
OL,9,Fimproving walking and cycling routes,
OL,10,Fmaking buildings more energy efficient
OL,11,Fand expanding the network of electric
OL,12,Fvehicle charging stations.
OL,14,FSusan Hall, the Conservative mayoral
OL,15,Fcandidate, said: "Promises are
OL,16,Fworthless from the man who has been
OL,17,Fdishonest with Londoners about his
OL,18,Fplans to tax drivers.
OL,26,@wD@ROU
