OL,3,CLondon mayor rules out expansion of
OL,4,CUlez if he stays in role after election
OL,6,F"Sadiq Khan said he wouldn't expand
OL,7,FUlez at the last election, then went
OL,8,Fahead and did the opposite.
OL,10,F"He has spent #150 million building
OL,11,Fthe technology for pay per mile, and
OL,12,Fnow wants us to believe he won't use
OL,13,Fit.
OL,15,F"Sadiq Khan is taking Londoners for
OL,16,Ffools and he just won't listen. That's
OL,17,Fwhy we need to vote for change on May
OL,18,F2."
