OL,6,FA spokesman for the mayor said: "Sadiq
OL,7,Fhas been clear that he has ruled out
OL,8,Fthe introduction of a pay-per-mile
OL,9,Froad user charging scheme but the
OL,10,FTories are clearly trying to mislead
OL,11,FLondoners by repeatedly saying this is
OL,12,Fnot the case.
OL,14,F"The mayor has now put in writing to
OL,15,Fthe TfL commissioner his clear pledge
OL,16,Fto London: no pay-per-mile scheme will
OL,17,Fbe introduced while he is mayor."
