OL,6,FLiberal Democrat candidate Rob Blackie
OL,7,Fsaid: "The Ulez could have been so
OL,8,Fmuch more successful if the mayor
OL,9,Fhadn't rushed the 2023 extension,
OL,10,Fgiving people in outer London just a
OL,11,Ffew months to adapt.
OL,13,F"If we're going to crack climate
OL,14,Fchange we need to bring people with us.
OL,16,F"It's crucial that the mayor focuses
OL,17,Fon fixing the problems that still
OL,18,Fpersist, especially for tradespeople
OL,19,Fwho need vans for work."
