OL,6,FGreen Party candidate Zoe Garbett
OL,7,Fsaid: "It's really disappointing that
OL,8,Fthe current Labour Mayor of London is
OL,9,Frefusing to listen to what Londoners
OL,10,Fare saying about Ulez.
OL,12,F"Whilst Greens absolutely support
OL,13,Faction to reduce air pollution, the
OL,14,Fmayor's current scheme has a lot of
OL,15,Funfairness built into it. I would work
OL,16,Fto tackle this.
