OL,3,CLondon mayor rules out expansion of
OL,4,CUlez if he stays in role after election
OL,6,F"London needs an improved system that
OL,7,Fwill bring down air pollution in a
OL,8,Ffairer way and I believe the best way
OL,9,Fto do that is to replace both the Ulez
OL,10,Fand congestion charge with a new road
OL,11,Fcharging system.
OL,13,F"At the moment, some of the worst
OL,14,Fpolluting vehicles are able to avoid
OL,15,Ffees whilst many people on low incomes
OL,16,Fin small older cars are being charged.
