OL,6,F"If elected, I would consult with
OL,7,FLondoners and start to develop a new
OL,8,Fsystem which takes into account the
OL,9,Fdistances driven, vehicle emissions,
OL,10,Ftime of day and location.
OL,12,F"I would also look for ways to take
OL,13,Finto account how many people are in
OL,14,Fthe car to encourage car sharing."
